Title: Honeywell Home DF06 resi pressure red valve d06f-b  25
Description: The DF06 spring-loaded pressure reducing valve (PRV) with 25mm male x male threaded connections operates via a force equalizing system, the force of a diaphragm operating against the force of an adjustment spring. Where outlet pressure (diaphragm force) falls because when water is drawn, the force of the spring opens the valve increasing outlet pressure until forces are equal. Suitable for use in household settings as well as for industrial or commercial applications, the DF06 protects installations against excessive pressure from the supply, avoiding damage and reducing water waste while minimising flow noise.
